> create a folder Pract6 on VS Code
> create a new folder in Pract6 named as public
> create a file in public folder as index.html --->  html:5
                                                     change title as Node JS
                                                     <body>
                                                          <h1> This is Static Web Page </h1>
                                                     </body>
                          

