-----------------------
> cd Pract6
> npm init
> Press ENTER
> Press ENTER
> This is WAD Pract6 Press ENTER
> Press ENTER
> Press ENTER
> Press ENTER
> Press ENTER
> author: Your_Name
> Press ENTER
> Press ENTER
> npm install express --save


VS Code:-
-------------
> click on folder
> new file (index.js)  --> const express=require('express');
                           const app=express();
                           app.use(express.static('public'))
                           app.listen(4000,()=>{
                             console.log("Server is Started");
                             })

Normal CommandPrompt:-
-----------------------
> node index.js


Open Chrome:-
---------------
in URL type ---> localhost:3000
